{
  "stem": "14156.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And my father said, yes, you have to fast.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "There's no buts about it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And when it came about 5 o'clock in the afternoon, I couldn't stand it.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I had to go out, and I threw up.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But my father go, oh, that's fine, that's OK.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "You can wait here until the service is over, and we all go together home.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And you'll, you'll be OK by the next day, don't worry about it.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] He guided me [SOB] very much that way.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We, yes, well, there was days, especially on a Sunday, when anybody else, you know, everybody else went to church there.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And Sunday we did not work, and he did not work either.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So we went out hiking.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "After we climbed up past the grapes, we were in the woods.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And summertime, we had, we could pick wild strawberries and wild blackberries.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he always looked for the clover leaves and looked for a four clover leaf.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Four-leaf clover who's supposed to bring luck.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And that's what he always looked for.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then we, we came walking back.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And that was like a Sunday.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, there was, there was sometimes things that the children always looked at me like I'm the Jew.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "OK.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They knew that.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And sometimes they come up with those stupid things, like you killed Jesus, things like that.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I just was buffed at those things, naturally, in the beginning.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And my father said-- they started fighting.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I was only a little guy, and three or four guys tried to gang up on me.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we had, we had two entrances.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Actually, the main entrance was on the house.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And then there was another one.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "It was like a cellar and had steel doors.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And he, he told me, get out, fight.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
